IN NO EVENT SHALL THE DEVELOPERS, CONTRIBUTORS, OR COPYRIGHT HOLDERS BE LIABLE FOR ANY CLAIM, DAMAGES, OR OTHER LIABILITY, WHETHER IN AN ACTION OF CONTRACT, TORT, OR OTHERWISE, ARISING FROM, OUT OF, IN CONNECTION WITH NEAM OR THE USE OR OTHER DEALINGS IN NEAM.

## Governing Law

This license shall be governed by and construed in accordance with international principles of software licensing, respecting national sovereignty and data protection requirements.

## Adoption and Authorization

Government entities wishing to deploy NEAM are encouraged to formally adopt the platform through appropriate administrative or legislative processes. Formal adoption enables access to classified security guidance, classified threat intelligence, and coordinated incident response support.

---

**This license ensures that NEAM remains a tool for sovereign governance, accountable to citizens through their elected representatives and protected from commercial exploitation or foreign influence.**
